/// Numpy Arrays Properties ///

/Attributes of an Array
1) Shape ( array.shape)
it return the shape of array in form of (row,column)

2) Size (array.size)
it return the total number of elements in an array (row*column)

3) ndim (array.ndim)
it return and tell which dimensional array it is..

4) dtype (array.dtype)
it return and tells the data type of element inside an array (int , float , str)

5) astype (array.astype( new_type )
it converts the element inside an array to a new data type


